                { \
                int c = '*'; \
                size_t n; \
                for ( n = 0; n < max_size && \
                             (c = getc( utap_in )) != EOF && c != '\n'; ++n ) \
                        buf[n] = (char) c; \
                if ( c == '\n' ) \
                        buf[n++] = (char) c; \
                if ( c == EOF && ferror( utap_in ) ) \
                        YY_FATAL_ERROR( "input in flex scanner failed" ); \
                result = n; \
                } \

                { \
                errno=0; \
